dagPlan.dagInfo:
{"description":"select i_brand_id brand_id, i_brand brand,t_hour,t_minute,
 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id
 ","context":"Hive"}

i_brand_id brand_id, i_brand brand,t_hour,t_minute,
 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id

 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute

 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id

i_brand_id brand_id, i_brand brand,t_hour,t_minute,
 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id

 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id

i_brand_id brand_id, i_brand brand,t_hour,t_minute,
 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id

{"config":{"hive.optimize.skewjoin.compiletime":"false","dfs.datanode.data.dir":"/workspace/storage/hdfs/hdfs_dn_dirs","mapred.output.committer.class":"org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.HiveFileFormatUtils$NullOutputCommitter","dfs.namenode.checkpoint.txns":"1000000","s3.replication":"3","hive.metastore.batch.retrieve.max":"300","mapreduce.output.fileoutputformat.compress.type":"RECORD","mapreduce.jobtracker.jobhistory.lru.cache.size":"5","hadoop.http.filter.initializers":"org.apache.hadoop.http.lib.StaticUserWebFilter","hive.autogen.columnalias.prefix.label":"_c","hive.map.aggr.hash.force.flush.memory.threshold":"0.9","hive.script.operator.id.env.var":"HIVE_SCRIPT_OPERATOR_ID","yarn.nodemanager.keytab":"/etc/krb5.keytab","hive.metastore.dml.events":"false","hive.convert.join.bucket.mapjoin.tez":"false","nfs.mountd.port":"4242","yarn.resourcemanager.zk-acl":"world:anyone:rwcda","_hive.local.session.path":"/tmp/ubuntu/8213a2da-cf30-4cee-ad04-c5f7eeab7eb3","dfs.https.server.keystore.resource":"ssl-server.xml","mapreduce.reduce.skip.maxgroups":"0","hive.tez.exec.print.summary":"false","hive.server2.thrift.max.message.size":"104857600","yarn.nodemanager.disk-health-checker.max-disk-utilization-per-disk-percentage":"98","yarn.nodemanager.localizer.client.thread-count":"5","ha.failover-controller.new-active.rpc-timeout.ms":"60000","ha.health-monitor.check-interval.ms":"1000","hive.compute.query.using.stats":"false","dfs.namenode.path.based.cache.block.map.allocation.percent":"0.25","dfs.namenode.checkpoint.period":"3600","hive.spark.client.connect.timeout":"1000ms","datanucleus.validateConstraints":"false","hive.explain.user":"false","hive.in.test":"false","mapreduce.jobtracker.taskcache.levels":"2","s3.stream-buffer-size":"4096","mapreduce.workflow.name":"select i_brand_id brand_id, i_brand brand,t_hour,t_minute,
 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk

i_brand_id brand_id, i_brand brand,t_hour,t_minute,
 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')

 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id

 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id

 	sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item JOIN (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute

                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2001
                 ) tmp ON tmp.sold_item_sk = item.i_item_sk
 JOIN time_dim ON tmp.time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk
 where
       i_manager_id=1
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id
